*Type 77 Infantry Gun  ([[Bofors 40 mm]] /Bofors 50 mm gun) - adopted in 1934 <ref>{{cite web|url=http://artydiv.com/2013-06-28-22-33-08/%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%92%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%B7%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%83%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%8D%E0%B9%88/item/463-%E0%B8%9E-%E0%B8%A8-2477-%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%B7%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%83%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%8D%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%9A-%E0%B9%81%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%9A-77.html|title=พ.ศ. 2477 ปืนใหญ่ทหารราบแบบ 77|language=Thai|work=Artillery Division, Fort Phibunsongkram, Lopburi|accessdate=29 June 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921144854/http://artydiv.com/%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%92%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%B7%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%83%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%8D%E0%B9%88/item/463-%E0%B8%9E-%E0%B8%A8-2477-%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%B7%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%83%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%8D%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%9A-%E0%B9%81%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%9A-77.html#|archive-date=2017-09-21|dead-url=no|df=}}</ref>

